    "Most foundries will provide integrated lasers, with the WPE exceeding 20%.",
    "Both multi-wavelength lasers and tunable lasers will be supported.",
    "• Silicon photonics will finally diversify beyond pluggable transceivers to other successful commercial products, finding wide adoption for CPO and xPU applications.",
